    <h2 id="why-elderberry-kids">Why Parents Are Choosing Elderberry Gummies for Children's Immune Support</h2>

    <p>During the average school year, children experience 6-8 upper respiratory infections — a number that doubles for kids in daycare or preschool. Each illness means missed school days, disrupted routines, and the worry that every parent knows. Elderberry (Sambucus nigra) has emerged as the most popular natural immune supplement for children, driven by emerging clinical evidence, a strong safety profile, and a delivery format that kids actually enjoy taking.</p>

